{"tid":2147843,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果將香港政府官員拍成荷里活電影","createTime":"2020-08-09T13:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T04:16:37.000Z","uid":69866,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3de2cd93ee2d266e3c6f7d229c5552bda6766808","tid":2147843,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T13:41:11.000Z","msg":"以政府官員的第一身角度去拍攝<br />\n用高科技同中共官員密談<br />\n會見民建聯， 圓桌會議<br />\n<br />\n夾雜下啲動作畫面。例如call個仔即刻離開美國。講個仔逃避FBI追殺，開快艇走<br />\n<br />\n講官員即刻轉走哂啲資金，深夜一點幾仲打緊份新聞稿<br />\n教育局長出手DQ題目，評審局開密會個個爆粗扔筆<br />\n<br />\n政治局不斷係部電腦改字眼，最終接到個無來電call : you are fired. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(當然演員同對白都係荷里活明星同英文) <br />\n<br />\n參考劇照：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B7hzvmG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB7hzvmG.jpg&h=c89324aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5Ha5B1H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5Ha5B1H.jpg&h=2ef2c1aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PdLxg1K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPdLxg1K.jpg&h=b3f19369&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tv5mamL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftv5mamL.jpg&h=469d6feb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qb0UvmN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqb0UvmN.png&h=46408571&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LmeVeOt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLmeVeOt.jpg&h=4928f8d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YcRc1tu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYcRc1tu.jpg&h=b862e614&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6bee49dc8345d2bd015bec5d4e8100fa4141719f","tid":2147843,"uid":134739,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T18:16:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x9TKT1O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx9TKT1O.jpg&h=bf782356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />師傅一年前已經同我講過， 佢話「<span class=\"green\">冇人會想睇</span>，但唔可以太劇烈運動，加上餵人奶要食番多啲嘢，如果唔係唔夠奶。」"},{"pid":"18dd4580c8bf80b16ce27d23074e159e3e9cae66","tid":2147843,"uid":290585,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T18:18:35.000Z","msg":"正呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"033c36b61caeedaf2e428ae3862da8ac94746c73","tid":2147843,"uid":69866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T04:16:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/JRX4QXIDEOM5V26BF2BL6LYOPQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2FJRX4QXIDEOM5V26BF2BL6LYOPQ%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminNUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=fee0f5b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200810%2FJRX4QXIDEOM5V26BF2BL6LYOPQ%2F&h=e64458ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200810/JRX4QXIDEOM5V26BF2BL6LYOPQ/</a>"}]}